      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC addresses how fast MD5 can be implemented in software and hardware, and whether it supports currently available IP bandwidth.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
